title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 143: Featuring Alex Killorn, Jason Demers and Kent Huskins
description:
On Mondays episode of Spittin' Chiclets the guys are joined by Alex Killorn of the Tampa Bay Lightning. The guys discuss Alex's career, some stories about his teammates and much more. The boys were also joined by Jason Demers and his good buddy Kent Huskins to talk some NHL, Kent's coffee shop, some good stories and a bunch more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
